industry_groups: Commerce and Shopping, Financial Services
full_description:
Burnt Finance is a decentralized auction protocol to enable fast and seamless auctions for a diverse array of assets. It provides an intuitive interface for minting new assets. These assets can be synthetics, NFTs, and even new digital assets. In less than a few minutes a user can mint a new asset and set up an entirely decentralized auction. Burnt allows users to customize their auctions which allows asset minting and trading to take place in a completely permissionless ecosystem.

It is based in Solana Beach, California.

description: Reply to buy text messaging for consumer brands.
industry_groups: Commerce and Shopping
full_description:
Reply to buy texting messaging for consumer brands.

Text products to your customers and they just reply to buy. It's the fastest and easiest way customers can buy from anywhere.

Here's how it works:

1. Brands text customers a product

2. Customers reply to buy

3. Brands fulfill the orders

Buddy's end-to-end platform has everything you need to grow your online business with text messaging. Build your contact list, sell products with reply to buy text messages, streamline order management and fulfillment, manage sales taxes, and track performance. 

Don't wait for customers to visit your site. Push the right products directly to their phones and let them purchase instantly with Reply to Buy.

It's mobile commerce, made easy.

description: Booyah Advertising is a full-service digital marketing agency based in Denver, CO.
industries: Advertising, Creative Agency, Digital Marketing, Digital Media, Marketing, SEO
industry_groups: Advertising, Content and Publishing, Internet Services, Media and Entertainment, Sales and Marketing
full_description:
Booyah Advertising is a digital marketing agency based in Denver, CO. We partner with companies who believe in using digital to drive their business forward. Our service offerings include Paid Search Advertising, Paid Social Advertising, Display and Video Advertising, Amazon Advertising, SEO, Content Marketing, and Creative. Transparent andforthright in our approach, we care about making your campaigns work. A lot. Data is our foundation for every decision, from media planning to creative design, and we assign trackable KPIs to even the most nebulous tactics. We'll always tell you what's working and what's not.
With real, straightforward relationships at the core of what we do, we manage over $100M in media each year for brands like Western Union, Unilever, Dish, Discover Card, Dice.com, Aspen Skiing Company, and Shane Co. We've also worked with hundreds of local brands, startups, and one-person shops with more modest budgets. It's hard to sum up what makes Booyah different. But when you know it, you know it. It's what keeps our clients and employees sticking around year after year. It might be how evidently we sweat the little details. It might be our jovial and supportive culture. Maybe it's our Western earnestness. Whatever "it" is for your brand, you will find a diligent partner in Booyah. If it seems we're both going the same places, let's go there together.

description: Better Home Serve, “Bringing Peace to Your Home”

full_description:
At Better Home Serve, we understand how much pride there is in owning your own home.  However, home ownership can be painful at times, if your home has not had the proper maintenance performed on it.  Better Home Serve’s mission is to take the pain out of home ownership, so you can relax with your family and friends knowing that your home maintenance has been taken care of.
There are many home warranty programs out there that will fix your problems after they have occurred.  With Better Home Serve, the goal is to avoid these costly mistakes by taking care of what needs to be taken care of annually.
We are here to make your home ownership easier for you.  We would love to hear about any additional issues you are having in your home so we can provide a fast pain free solution.
Better Home Serve, “Bringing Peace to Your Home”
